<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">The Food and Drug Administration’s 2022 inspection of the Sun Pharma factory in India warned of contaminations and deficiencies. But the plant received permission from the FDA to continue shipping more than a dozen generic medications to Americans.</span>
    
        <span class="attribution__credit">
