                        <p>We are still reporting. <strong>If you are a current or former FDA employee or someone in the industry with information about the agency, the safety of generic drugs, or the manufacturers that make them, our team wants to hear from you.</strong> Megan Rose can be reached on Signal or WhatsApp at 202-805-4865. Debbie Cenziper can be reached on Signal or WhatsApp at 301-222-3133. You can also email us at <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#36707277764644594643545a5f555718594451"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="490f0d0809393b26393c2b25202a2867263b2e">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>.</p>

