            <div class="rich-byline__info">
                <div class="stack stack--row">
                    <a class="rich-byline__name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/irena-hwang">Irena Hwang</a>

                                    </div>

                                    <p class="rich-byline__bio-short">I covered public health and the agencies that oversee it, including the FDA and CDC.</p>

                
                <ul class="rich-byline__more">
