    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://projects.propublica.org/nih-cuts-research-lost-trump/">
                                    Shattered Science: The Research Lost as Trump Targets NIH Funding
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The Trump administration cut research funding that sought cures for future pandemics, examined the causes of dementia and tried to prevent HIV transmission. ProPublica heard from more than 150 researchers to understand the work that’s been lost.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/annie-waldman">Annie Waldman</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/asia-fields">Asia Fields</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/ashley-clarke">Ashley Clarke</a>, design by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/zisiga-mukulu">Zisiga Mukulu</a>, and photography by <span class="name">Bethany Mollenkof</span> for <a href="https://www.propublica.org">ProPublica</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-06-12EDT07:00">June 12, 2025, 7 a.m. EDT</time>
