    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/why-americans-pay-more-for-prescription-drugs">
                                    Why Do Americans Pay More for Prescription Drugs?
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Drug companies in the U.S. face few restraints on what to charge for their products. A bipartisan bill would penalize those companies that sell their drugs at higher prices than the average of the prices in other wealthy nations.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/david-armstrong">David Armstrong</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-05-09EDT05:00">May 9, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </span>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></div> </div> </div>
